&gt; keep anyone but themselves playing on the server. 

&gt; Read Tarquins post, it appears some see the world of EQ as 
&gt; nothing more than xp numbers and obstacles in their way of 
&gt; dominating other players. 

&gt; I agree this wouldn't have worked on a pvp server. In almost 
